ddiction. Alternatives like renewables and nuclear power must be allowed to become the dominant component of our energy mix,\" said Huhne.\nThis news comes to light as , a rival energy company to British Gas, announced last month their intentions to up the prices of their electricity and gas supplies by ten and nineteen per cent respectively."}
